title: Buffy the Vampire Slayer & Angel Unofficial Soundtrack
description:
This is (almost) every song ever played in both Buffy the Vampire Slayer and Angel series. This is not my work (see .nfo for original description & track list) and all credit goes to the original creator. I had a tough time finding seeds for this one ~7 years later so I decided to reup it to a few places. The amount of work put into this is astounding and I would hate to see it die.




NOTE: It is missing the original "Goodies" folder that is an additional 20.7 GB because these were just random albums from some of the artists that had nothing to do with either show
